   <directions>
      <step><![CDATA[dissolve in 320 ml water, warm, 5m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[add flour bit by bit and knead, 10m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[rest in greased bowl, covered in kitchen towel until doubled in size, 2h]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[sauté in 2 tbs oil, olive on hot until just golden, 1m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[sauté until just wilted, 3m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Drain, squeeze well keeping the water, and chop corasely]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[(if using) soak in spinach water, 10m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[drain and add to chopped spinach]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[add chili powder if using]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[add olives, mozzarella if using]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[If using sausage, sauté in 2 tbs oil, olive on med, 4m]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[add until until seared, 2]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Mix all the fillings together in a bowl]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Roll out dough as thin as possible, smear oil over it, lay the stuffing over it. Start rolling, smearing more oil between layers of dough]]></step>
      <step><![CDATA[Bake until ready on 190°, 35m]]></step>
   </directions>
